tests/gherkin_features/deontological_reasoning_callables/README.md:7:These Gherkin files provide behavioral specifications for deontological reasoning functionality used in legal and ethical analysis. Each file explicitly tests a single callable method and uses concrete scenarios with minimal adverbs and adjectives.
